data.description:
3 bedroom 2bath home with office in Robinson ISD on 1.82 Acres!  Has hay shed, large storage building, and oversized two car carport that current owner used with panels to keep livestock.  Also great to store camper.  The property is cross fenced for livestock and has a stall set up there also.  In addition, there is a chicken coop, an oversized coved patio, and a 1 car attached garage with extra workshop space.  New roof is coming Aug 2023.  This home qualifies for zero down USDA Financing W.A.C.
**Seller is offering $5000 towards buyers closing cost or to buy down their interest rate with approved offer.
***Zero down USDA Financing with approved credit.
